======================================================================
General commands

List of commands:

cv addenergy <E>
cv bias
cv colvar
cv config <conf>
cv configfile <conf_file>
cv delete
cv frame [frame]
cv getconfig
cv getenergy
cv help [command]
cv list [param]
cv listcommands
cv load <prefix>
cv loadfromstring <buffer>
cv molid [molid]
cv printframe
cv printframelabels
cv reset
cv resetindexgroups
cv save <prefix>
cv savetostring
cv units [units]
cv update
cv version

For detailed help on each command use:
    cv help <command>

To list all commands acting on collective variables use:
    cv help colvar

To list all commands acting on biases use:
    cv help bias

======================================================================
